OL,4,CHorse-racing bosses condemn abattoir
OL,5,Cfootage
OL,6, Irish and British horse-racing
OL,7, authorities have condemned footage that
OL,8, revealed evidence of a UK abattoir
OL,9, breaking welfare rules when
OL,10, slaughtering former race horses.
OL,12,FHorse Racing Ireland said the footage -
OL,13,Fwhich featured in a BBC Panorama
OL,14,Finvestigation - was abhorrent.
OL,16,FThe British Horseracing Authority (BHA)
OL,17,Fmet welfare experts earlier to discuss
OL,18,Fthe issue "as a matter of urgency".
OL,20,FThe abattoir told the BBC it did not
OL,21,Faccept any form of animal abuse.
